Combined effect of antimicrobial coating and gamma irradiation on shelf life 
extension of pre-cooked shrimp (Penaeus spp.).

Ouattara B(1), Sabato SF, Lacroix M.

Author information:
(1)Canadian Irradiarian Center, Research Center in Microbiology and 
