trans-cinnamaldehyde. No detrimental effects of gamma irradiation on 
organoleptic parameters (appearance, odor, and taste) were observed. However, 
incorporation of thyme oil and trans-cinnamaldehyde reduced the acceptability 
scores for taste and odor.

